32:36.800 --> 32:38.723
LEAH: It was like a switch went off.

32:39.040 --> 32:41.260
There was something in his eyes.

32:41.360 --> 32:43.362
I've never seen anything
like that, ever.

32:45.000 --> 32:46.940
Well, have you ever
felt threatened by him before?

32:47.040 --> 32:48.087
