37:49.680 --> 37:50.681
DETECTIVE HANSEN: Miss Vaughn?

37:51.800 --> 37:53.564
Have a seat, please.

37:55.360 --> 37:58.540
- So, you think someone is stalking you?
- Yes.

37:58.640 --> 38:01.420
